{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":965,"text":"I was born and raised in North Korea."},{"time":4468,"text":"Although my family constantly struggled against poverty,"},{"time":9268,"text":"I was always loved and cared for first,"},{"time":12796,"text":"because I was the only son"},{"time":14947,"text":"and the youngest of two in the family."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18117,"text":"But then the great famine began in 1994."},{"time":21724,"text":"I was four years old."},{"time":24183,"text":"My sister and I would go searching for firewood"},{"time":27980,"text":"starting at 5 in the morning"},{"time":29956,"text":"and come back after midnight."},{"time":32762,"text":"I would wander the streets searching for food,"},{"time":36650,"text":"and I remember seeing a small child"},{"time":38823,"text":"tied to a mother's back eating chips,"},{"time":41645,"text":"and wanting to steal them from him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44869,"text":"Hunger is humiliation. Hunger is hopelessness."},{"time":49702,"text":"For a hungry child, politics and freedom"},{"time":52905,"text":"are not even thought of."},{"time":55657,"text":"On my ninth birthday, my parents"},{"time":58345,"text":"couldn't give me any food to eat."},{"time":61774,"text":"But even as a child, I could feel the heaviness"},{"time":65718,"text":"in their hearts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68753,"text":"Over a million North Koreans died of starvation in that time,"},{"time":73968,"text":"and in 2003, when I was 13 years old,"},{"time":77664,"text":"my father became one of them."},{"time":80577,"text":"I saw my father wither away and die."},{"time":84465,"text":"In the same year, my mother disappeared one day,"},{"time":88597,"text":"and then my sister told me"},{"time":90402,"text":"that she was going to China to earn money,"},{"time":93003,"text":"but that she would return with money and food soon."},{"time":97198,"text":"Since we had never been separated,"},{"time":100149,"text":"and I thought we would be together forever,"},{"time":103119,"text":"I didn't even give her a hug when she left."},{"time":106992,"text":"It was the biggest mistake I have ever made in my life."},{"time":111205,"text":"But again, I didn't know"},{"time":112916,"text":"it was going to be a long goodbye."},{"time":116404,"text":"I have not seen my mom or my sister since then."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121341,"text":"Suddenly, I became an orphan and homeless."},{"time":125560,"text":"My daily life became very hard,"},{"time":128649,"text":"but very simple."},{"time":130701,"text":"My goal was to find a dusty piece of bread in the trash."},{"time":134724,"text":"But that is no way to survive."},{"time":137631,"text":"I started to realize, begging would not be the solution."},{"time":142349,"text":"So I started to steal from food carts in illegal markets."},{"time":147675,"text":"Sometimes, I found small jobs"},{"time":150640,"text":"in exchange for food."},{"time":152970,"text":"Once, I even spent two months in the winter"},{"time":156116,"text":"working in a coal mine,"},{"time":157859,"text":"33 meters underground without any protection"},{"time":163634,"text":"for up to 16 hours a day."},{"time":167067,"text":"I was not uncommon."},{"time":169431,"text":"Many other orphans survived this way, or worse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176992,"text":"When I could not fall asleep from bitter cold"},{"time":181128,"text":"or hunger pains,"},{"time":182595,"text":"I hoped that, the next morning,"},{"time":185443,"text":"my sister would come back to wake me up"},{"time":188006,"text":"with my favorite food."},{"time":190276,"text":"That hope kept me alive."},{"time":193426,"text":"I don't mean big, grand hope."},{"time":196224,"text":"I mean the kind of hope that made me believe"},{"time":199346,"text":"that the next trash can had bread,"},{"time":201809,"text":"even though it usually didn't."},{"time":204942,"text":"But if I didn't believe it, I wouldn't even try,"},{"time":208385,"text":"and then I would die."},{"time":210478,"text":"Hope kept me alive."},{"time":214416,"text":"Every day, I told myself,"},{"time":217176,"text":"no matter how hard things got,"},{"time":219904,"text":"still I must live."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223806,"text":"After three years of waiting for my sister's return,"},{"time":227936,"text":"I decided to go to China to look for her myself."},{"time":232288,"text":"I realized"},{"time":235148,"text":"I couldn't survive much longer this way."},{"time":238798,"text":"I knew the journey would be risky,"},{"time":241603,"text":"but I would be risking my life either way."},{"time":244500,"text":"I could die of starvation like my father in North Korea,"},{"time":248686,"text":"or at least I could try for a better life"},{"time":252144,"text":"by escaping to China."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255380,"text":"I had learned that many people tried to cross"},{"time":258610,"text":"the border to China in the nighttime to avoid being seen."},{"time":263397,"text":"North Korean border guards often shoot and kill people"},{"time":267355,"text":"trying to cross the border without permission."},{"time":270728,"text":"Chinese soldiers will catch"},{"time":273379,"text":"and send back North Koreans,"},{"time":275233,"text":"where they face severe punishment."},{"time":279573,"text":"I decided to cross during the day,"},{"time":282654,"text":"first because I was still a kid and scared of the dark,"},{"time":288087,"text":"second because I knew I was already taking a risk,"},{"time":292736,"text":"and since not many people tried to cross during the day,"},{"time":296151,"text":"I thought I might be able to cross"},{"time":297841,"text":"without being seen by anyone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301266,"text":"I made it to China on February 15, 2006."},{"time":305174,"text":"I was 16 years old."},{"time":307402,"text":"I thought things in China would be easier,"},{"time":310322,"text":"since there was more food."},{"time":313595,"text":"I thought more people would help me."},{"time":316651,"text":"But it was harder than living in North Korea,"},{"time":320664,"text":"because I was not free."},{"time":322359,"text":"I was always worried about being caught"},{"time":325104,"text":"and sent back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327899,"text":"By a miracle, some months later,"},{"time":331170,"text":"I met someone who was running"},{"time":332613,"text":"an underground shelter for North Koreans,"},{"time":335955,"text":"and was allowed to live there"},{"time":338563,"text":"and eat regular meals for the first time in many years."},{"time":343915,"text":"Later that year, an activist helped me escape China"},{"time":348396,"text":"and go to the United States as a refugee."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352617,"text":"I went to America without knowing a word of English,"},{"time":355917,"text":"yet my social worker told me that I had to go to high school."},{"time":360296,"text":"Even in North Korea, I was an F student."},{"time":364495,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":365879,"text":"And I barely finished elementary school."},{"time":369586,"text":"And I remember I fought in school more than once a day."},{"time":372890,"text":"Textbooks and the library were not my playground."},{"time":376828,"text":"My father tried very hard to motivate me into studying,"},{"time":380573,"text":"but it didn't work."},{"time":383124,"text":"At one point, my father gave up on me."},{"time":386267,"text":"He said, \"You're not my son anymore.\""},{"time":390236,"text":"I was only 11 or 12, but it hurt me deeply."},{"time":394988,"text":"But nevertheless, my level of motivation"},{"time":397649,"text":"still didn't change before he died."},{"time":402356,"text":"So in America, it was kind of ridiculous"},{"time":405161,"text":"that they said I should go to high school."},{"time":408188,"text":"I didn't even go to middle school."},{"time":410612,"text":"I decided to go, just because they told me to,"},{"time":413996,"text":"without trying much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":416404,"text":"But one day, I came home and my foster mother"},{"time":419817,"text":"had made chicken wings for dinner."},{"time":423026,"text":"And during dinner, I wanted to have one more wing,"},{"time":426280,"text":"but I realized there were not enough for everyone,"},{"time":429476,"text":"so I decided against it."},{"time":432973,"text":"When I looked down at my plate,"},{"time":435298,"text":"I saw the last chicken wing, that my foster father had given me his."},{"time":440434,"text":"I was so happy."},{"time":442752,"text":"I looked at him sitting next to me."},{"time":445015,"text":"He just looked back at me very warmly,"},{"time":448331,"text":"but said no words."},{"time":451003,"text":"Suddenly I remembered my biological father."},{"time":455847,"text":"My foster father's small act of love"},{"time":458820,"text":"reminded me of my father,"},{"time":461041,"text":"who would love to share his food with me"},{"time":464041,"text":"when he was hungry, even if he was starving."},{"time":468678,"text":"I felt so suffocated that I had so much food in America,"},{"time":473010,"text":"yet my father died of starvation."},{"time":476477,"text":"My only wish that night was to cook a meal for him,"},{"time":480680,"text":"and that night I also thought of what else I could do"},{"time":484171,"text":"to honor him."},{"time":486387,"text":"And my answer was to promise to myself"},{"time":489121,"text":"that I would study hard and get the best education"},{"time":492551,"text":"in America to honor his sacrifice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":496115,"text":"I took school seriously,"},{"time":498651,"text":"and for the first time ever in my life,"},{"time":501451,"text":"I received an academic award for excellence,"},{"time":505348,"text":"and made dean's list from the first semester in high school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510962,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":518594,"text":"That chicken wing changed my life."},{"time":521324,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":525381,"text":"Hope is personal. Hope is something"},{"time":528973,"text":"that no one can give to you."},{"time":531482,"text":"You have to choose to believe in hope."},{"time":534402,"text":"You have to make it yourself."},{"time":537569,"text":"In North Korea, I made it myself."},{"time":540809,"text":"Hope brought me to America."},{"time":543522,"text":"But in America, I didn't know what to do,"},{"time":546522,"text":"because I had this overwhelming freedom."},{"time":551554,"text":"My foster father at that dinner gave me a direction,"},{"time":555605,"text":"and he motivated me and gave me a purpose"},{"time":559131,"text":"to live in America."}]},{"cues":[{"time":563058,"text":"I did not come here by myself."},{"time":566178,"text":"I had hope, but hope by itself is not enough."},{"time":571132,"text":"Many people helped me along the way to get here."},{"time":575286,"text":"North Koreans are fighting hard to survive."},{"time":579274,"text":"They have to force themselves to survive,"},{"time":582063,"text":"have hope to survive,"},{"time":584818,"text":"but they cannot make it without help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589579,"text":"This is my message to you."},{"time":591925,"text":"Have hope for yourself,"},{"time":594634,"text":"but also help each other."},{"time":597746,"text":"Life can be hard for everyone, wherever you live."},{"time":604328,"text":"My foster father didn't intend to change my life."},{"time":608114,"text":"In the same way, you may also change someone's life"},{"time":612486,"text":"with even the smallest act of love."},{"time":617006,"text":"A piece of bread can satisfy your hunger,"},{"time":622124,"text":"and having the hope will bring you bread"},{"time":625225,"text":"to keep you alive."},{"time":627510,"text":"But I confidently believe that"},{"time":630727,"text":"your act of love and caring"},{"time":634185,"text":"can also save another Joseph's life"},{"time":637589,"text":"and change thousands of other Josephs"},{"time":643031,"text":"who are still having hope to survive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":647033,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":648340,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":684561,"text":"Adrian Hong: Joseph, thank you for sharing"},{"time":687386,"text":"that very personal and special story with us."},{"time":690568,"text":"I know you haven't seen your sister for, you said,"},{"time":693793,"text":"it was almost exactly a decade,"},{"time":696253,"text":"and in the off chance that she may be able to see this,"},{"time":698670,"text":"we wanted to give you an opportunity"},{"time":700497,"text":"to send her a message."}]},{"cues":[{"time":702725,"text":"Joseph Kim: In Korean?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":703861,"text":"AH: You can do English, then Korean as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":706469,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":710377,"text":"JK: Okay, I'm not going to make it any longer in Korean"},{"time":712718,"text":"because I don't think I can make it"},{"time":715459,"text":"without tearing up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":719115,"text":"Nuna, it has been already 10 years"},{"time":723836,"text":"that I haven’t seen you."},{"time":730357,"text":"I just wanted to say"},{"time":733749,"text":"that I miss you, and I love you,"},{"time":737933,"text":"and please come back to me and stay alive."},{"time":742276,"text":"And I -- oh, gosh."},{"time":747162,"text":"I still haven't given up my hope to see you."},{"time":753591,"text":"I will live my life happily"},{"time":758253,"text":"and study hard"},{"time":761572,"text":"until I see you,"},{"time":763649,"text":"and I promise I will not cry again."},{"time":768228,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":769785,"text":"Yes, I'm just looking forward to seeing you,"},{"time":772373,"text":"and if you can't find me,"},{"time":774644,"text":"I will also look for you,"},{"time":777716,"text":"and I hope to see you one day."},{"time":780452,"text":"And can I also make a small message to my mom?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":783788,"text":"AH: Sure, please."}]},{"cues":[{"time":785439,"text":"JK: I haven't spent much time with you,"},{"time":788228,"text":"but I know that you still love me,"},{"time":790140,"text":"and you probably still pray for me"},{"time":793084,"text":"and think about me."},{"time":796204,"text":"I just wanted to say thank you"},{"time":798356,"text":"for letting me be in this world."},{"time":801890,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":803359,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}